game_description: EYOWL - Indoor cycling sessions. Get ready to work up a sweat, have fun and get fit. Itâ€™s as easy as getting on your indoor bike, putting on your headset and pedalling. Eyowl supports hand tracking, so no controllers needed during your sessions. Every bike is supported, even if it's not connected at all. Streaming indoor cycling sessions with top instructors, good music, great graphics and full immersion for your workout.
Languages: English, English (Australia), English (UK), English (US), English (Canada), English (South Africa)
review_1: 1. I wish I understand the coach in front of you (no caption for Deaf people like me). 2. Chill with all that talking. I wanna ride my bike and enjoy the scenery. 3. What the heck are those see thru boxes floating to me from left to my right? Am I supposed to punch them or something? 4. Don't think I can pause this app? Bluetooth needs say what it is not all that bunch of numbers. Overall, it is ok. I love the concept of turning the level of bike 1-5 which is cool. Always a room for an improvement.
